JUNCTION_POINTS: Points where flowlines converge or diverge
IGO_METRIC_VIEW: Riverscape metrics summarized onto integrated geographic objects (IGO) points using a moving window analysis (intermediate data product only)
DGO_METRIC_VIEW: Riverscape metrics summarized within and attributed onto discrete geographic object (DGO) polygons (intermediate data product only)
RME_DGO: Discrete geographic objects (DGO) polygon geometries for storing RME attributes (intermediate data product only)
RME_IGO: Integrated geographic objects (IGO) point geometries for storing RME moving window attributes (intermediate data product only)
DGO_METRICS: Riverscape metrics summarized within and attributed onto discrete geographic object (DGO) polygons
IGO_METRICS: Riverscape metrics summarized onto integrated geographic objects (IGO) points using a moving window analysis
DGO_MEASUREMENTS: Measurements taken from DEM input stored for each DGO
